id":"ae9d3c86df1008ec893a165c01cfffa27009a75e","tid":527014,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"帶佢去睇獸醫"},{"pid":"d7ab20e3ba1241e41577ffa3698b0f173b255d74","tid":527014,"uid":104213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/182852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F182852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c1794e63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19151690041b4718d5c575cf8526d3b4b4656569","tid":527014,"uid":57255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"波台友又走黎感情台搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7ace2b202fa0279f9158cd470ea374c4b394cc","tid":527014,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:33:25.000Z","msg":"雖然樓主轉貼 但篇野真文黎嫁<br />\n<br />\n唔好屈人作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c0b3e5e9c642e8504e2e1c7d054f029f5b89a3","tid":527014,"uid":54777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e866739c4d64a1f4953fd53bae606e3e5815d8","tid":527014,"uid":38904,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下背景先 差唔多一年前左右 我就上網識左個絲打<br />\n同我都幾<span style=\"color: red;\">岩</span>傾 咁好快就交換左電話 之後我同佢幾乎日日都whatsapp<br />\n唔夠兩星期我地就約左出黎見面 見到面之後覺得佢都幾靚女 19歲左右 細細粒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地住得好近 之後每星期我地起碼一星期見一次 出黎睇戲食飯<span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span><br />\n一個月之後我地就一齊左 本身我都諗住同玩下就算 當拍下散拖屌下靚囡囡都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢話唔想咁快扑住 咁我同佢都叫一齊左 無理由無得屌就即刻飛左佢咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span>佢每次上黎我屋企 我都叫佢比我扑 佢每次都say no<br />\n我叫左佢半年 佢先肯幫我打個飛機 搞到我都想飛左佢<br />\n不過佢叫我等下 話好愛我 一定會比我 不過未有心理準備 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span>我算啦 就等多兩個月 如果都仲<span style=\"color: red;\">系</span>唔得就飛左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直至去到中秋 個日咁啱都<span style=\"color: red;\">系</span>佢20歲生日<br />\n食完生日飯 <span style=\"color: red;\">系</span>街行<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>陣 本身<span style=\"color: red;\">個</span>日都諗住講分手算<br />\n點知佢話有驚喜<span style=\"color: red;\">比</span>我 拖<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>我上佢屋企 <br />\n上到佢屋企 佢拎左個dom出黎 話佢已經ready 想同我黎第一次<br />\n我等<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>成大半年 我即刻話好 同佢翻雲覆雨啦<br />\n完<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>第一次之後好似開發左佢咁 又大食 成日都話要 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲</span>開始同我講人世<span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span> 話結婚之後點點點 又生小朋友又依樣<span style=\"color: red;\">個</span>樣<br />\n大佬<span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span>我諗住同佢玩下就算 屌到厭就飛架啦 <span style=\"color: red;\">系吾系</span>先<br />\n我就唔理佢 每次佢講親都敷衍下就上床扑野算<br />\n<br />\n咁重點黎啦 早排 佢話佢安全期 想試下唔戴套中出<br />\n作為男人 有靚囡囡叫你可以中出 邊個會唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都驚有BB 就同佢講如果有左我唔會負責架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span>佢都話唔怕 就算有<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>都唔會迫我負責任 而且信我愛佢唔會拋妻棄子<br />\n之後我買左粒事後丸比佢 但佢又唔肯食話好怕傷身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁早排我同個女仔friend飲酒 飲左幾杯之後個女仔叫我送佢返屋企<br />\n佢<span style=\"color: red;\">系咁</span>引誘我 話屋企無人 又<span style=\"color: red;\">系咁</span>摸我 咁我又開始有D玩厭我女朋友<span style=\"color: red;\"> 咁</span>都想下同其他人玩下<br />\n我就拖住佢上佢屋企 點知去到個女仔friend屋企附近 咁岩見到我女朋友經過<br />\n佢即刻上前問我同個女仔friend咩事 我都唔想多講加上酒精上腦 即刻同個女仔friend打個茄輪 同我女朋友講有第二個 要同佢分手<br />\n佢就喊住跑走左 我地就緊<span style=\"color: red;\">系</span>唔撚理佢 上樓扑野啦<br />\n<br />\n去到上個星期 我都已經無再同女朋友聯絡過 <br />\n3日前 佢上黎我屋企 比條驗孕棒我睇 話有<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span><br />\n咁我緊<span style=\"color: red;\">系</span>唔理佢啦 都分左手 仲要本身講明唔會負責<br />\n佢話要同我結婚 生個仔落黎 又話唔再追究我之前有第二個<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\">系甘</span>叫佢走都<span style=\"color: red;\">吾</span>肯走 煩到我火到黎 我一把打落佢塊面到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">系</span>銀包掉左3000比佢 叫佢上深圳落左佢唔好再煩我 一野就推佢出屋企門口<br />\n但依幾日仲不斷<span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span>whatsapp我 打<span style=\"color: red;\">比</span>我 真<span style=\"color: red;\">系</span>好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都<span style=\"color: red;\">吾</span>知佢<span style=\"color: red;\">系吾系</span>食左我個$3000 無去落仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟點先可以趕走佢唔好再煩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母練吓仔先啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"唔洗爭，你都要去練字"},{"pid":"8e24481d5e16782e53fc96b49fa56c84b272209c","tid":527014,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"743acd205a113babef9c47384d33ebac2a032dfb","tid":527014,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:05:31.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball"},{"pid":"37d83e22b95ce0b1d79425d01cbe06ab91a88826","tid":527014,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab7ace2b202fa0279f9158cd470ea374c4b394cc","tid":527014,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:33:25.000Z","msg":"雖然樓主轉貼 但篇野真文黎嫁<br />\n<br />\n唔好屈人作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"咪又係過街老鼠波台狗"},{"pid":"3c9fe4268308f887b856f561fa4ab10baf7e2b97","tid":527014,"uid":99364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4358a3af5607317a26f773965ab3d711228c13a4","tid":527014,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"acd6cef5b7c2bb579806ea021262d9fe2d2c2f2a","tid":527014,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c34ab232afae391872674998ba6486f389c5bf","tid":527014,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"正必？"},{"pid":"0839f4a1244dc4befa59ab1a55bf08cd1d08e78b","tid":527014,"uid":108249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb81023c21d8038e7270b094f9418bac90c0143","tid":527014,"uid":48085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T11:46:32.000Z","msg":"俾你電話我，打俾你教你點做"},{"pid":"d9e90cdd82d8902d4f15a62cbefe64f3a0626dce","tid":527014,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"甘長典睇牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e833d0d0326e9d97738e9dfd41b2a26c703135","tid":527014,"uid":16462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:30:01.000Z","msg":"最後竟然唔係整電話 零分重作"},{"pid":"99210773193008f15468f501fb8dc03494db24d0","tid":527014,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e90cdd82d8902d4f15a62cbefe64f3a0626dce","tid":527014,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"甘長典睇牙<img